    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior shows noticeable signs of age, including several rust spots, deep scratches, and fading paint. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with some tearing, and several electronic components are currently non-functional. Mechanically, the car starts but runs roughly, indicating it is in need of immediate repairs to be fully roadworthy. This is an ideal project car for someone with the tools and time to restore it.",
