    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. The engine maintains peak volumetric efficiency with a crisp 8,400 RPM redline, supported by recent preventative rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacement. The chassis remains communicative, utilizing its M Variable Differential Lock and stiffened subframe bushings to ensure precise power delivery through the rear wheels. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and patina indicative of its road-going history, the mechanical vitals\u2014including the VANOS system and EDC dampers\u2014are in excellent working order, offering a visceral, high-compression driving experience.",
